OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe King is rolling out the red carpet
OL,7,Ffor the Nigerian president on
OL,8,FWednesday, as he hosts a state visit
OL,9,Fat Windsor Castle.
OL,11,FCharles will welcome Bola Ahmed Tinubu
OL,12,Fand his wife, Oluremi Tinubu, to a
OL,13,Fglittering state banquet in St
OL,14,FGeorge's Hall in their honour,
OL,15,Fattended by the Queen and the Prince
OL,16,Fand Princess of Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FIt is the first state visit to the UK
OL,7,Fby a leader of the west African nation
OL,8,Fin 37 years, and also the first
OL,9,Fincoming state visit by a Muslim
OL,10,Fleader during Ramadan in almost a
OL,11,Fcentury.
OL,13,FWilliam and Kate will be on duty
OL,14,Fduring the day, greeting the president
OL,15,Fand his wife at the luxury spa hotel
OL,16,FFairmont Windsor Park, on the edge of
OL,17,FWindsor Great Park, in the morning and
OL,18,Fescorting them to the town centre to
OL,19,Fformally meet the King and Camilla.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe King, the Queen, the Prince and
OL,7,FPrincess of Wales and Mr and Mrs
OL,8,FTinubu will then travel in a carriage
OL,9,Fprocession in a show of traditional
OL,10,Fpomp and pageantry through Windsor to
OL,11,Fthe castle's quadrangle to see the
OL,12,FGuard of Honour for the ceremonial
OL,13,Fwelcome.
OL,15,FThames Valley Police said extensive
OL,16,Fsecurity measures are being deployed
OL,17,Fin the Berkshire town, as the event
OL,18,Ftakes place against an international
OL,19,Fbackdrop of the deepening Middle East
OL,20,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
