PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe grand royal occasion comes less
OL,7,Fthan a month after the King's brother,
OL,8,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor, was
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of sharing
OL,10,Fconfidential reports with paedophile
OL,11,FJeffrey Epstein, amid the ongoing
OL,12,Fscandal facing the monarchy.
OL,14,FThe Sun reported that removal vans
OL,15,Fwere seen at Andrew's new home, Marsh
OL,16,FFarm on the King's Sandringham estate
OL,17,Fin Norfolk, on Monday, prompting
OL,18,Fspeculation the disgraced former
OL,19,Fprince was preparing to relocate from
OL,20,Fhis temporary home at Wood Farm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe president and the first lady
OL,7,Farrived in the UK on Tuesday on a
OL,8,FNigerian Air Force flight as
OL,9,Fscheduled, and were met at Stansted
OL,10,FAirport by the deputy lieutenant of
OL,11,FEssex, Mark Bevan, on behalf of the
OL,12,FKing.
OL,14,FTheir visit went ahead despite suicide
OL,15,Fbombings in north-eastern Nigeria's
OL,16,FBorno state on Monday, which killed 23
OL,17,Fpeople and injured more than 100.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
