PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FMr Tinubu condemned the "evil-minded"
OL,7,Fterror groups and said he mourned
OL,8,Fthose who lost their lives, saying
OL,9,F"Nigeria will not succumb to fear".
OL,11,FThe last Nigerian state visit to the
OL,12,FUK was in 1989, when Queen Elizabeth
OL,13,FII welcomed military ruler General
OL,14,FIbrahim Babangida to London.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@eO]qD@AOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
