OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThis time, the two-day visit falls at
OL,7,Fthe end of the holy month of Ramadan,
OL,8,Fduring which many Muslims fast and
OL,9,Frefrain from eating or drinking
OL,10,Fbetween dawn and sunset ` so there
OL,11,Fwill be no traditional lunch with the
OL,12,FKing in the castle for the president
OL,13,Fduring the day.
OL,15,FThe programme has been specially
OL,16,Fadapted, and Charles will receive the
OL,17,Fpresident during an audience in the
OL,18,Fafternoon instead of hosting the usual
OL,19,Fwelcome lunch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
