PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FIn 1928, Charles's great-grandfather
OL,7,FKing George V hosted King Amanullah
OL,8,FKhan of Afghanistan, for a three-day
OL,9,Fstate visit from March 13-15, when
OL,10,FRamadan fell between February 22 and
OL,11,FMarch 22 that year.
OL,13,FThere are no known records showing
OL,14,Fwhether or not King Amanullah observed
OL,15,FRamadan.
OL,17,FMr Tinubu will break his fast
OL,18,Fprivately at sunset on Wednesday
OL,19,Fbefore joining the King and Queen for
OL,20,Fthe night-time state banquet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
