PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe first lady, who is known as Remi,
OL,7,Fis a Christian and an ordained
OL,8,FPentecostal pastor.
OL,10,FEid-al-Fitr, the Islamic holiday
OL,11,Fcelebrating the end of Ramadan, begins
OL,12,Fon Thursday evening, when the
OL,13,Fpresident and his wife will leave the
OL,14,FUK.
OL,16,FThe King will also join the president
OL,17,Fand first lady in the castle's Vicars'
OL,18,FHall to meet organisations working on
OL,19,Finterfaith dialogue, on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
