CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe Nigerian leader's stay, aimed at
OL,7,Fstrengthening the UK's position as a
OL,8,Fglobal hub for African business,
OL,9,Fcoincides with the Department for
OL,10,FBusiness and Trade's announcement that
OL,11,Fhundreds of new jobs are to be created
OL,12,Fas a series of Nigerian companies
OL,13,Fscale up their operations in the UK.
OL,15,FIn 2024, the King's son, the Duke of
OL,16,FSussex, carried out a quasi-royal tour
OL,17,Fto Nigeria with the Duchess of Sussex,
OL,18,Fafter Meghan disclosed she was 43%
OL,19,FNigerian after a genealogy test.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
