PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773799382
OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FMrs Tinubu was later accused of
OL,7,Fcriticising Meghan's choice of
OL,8,Foutfits, when she gave a speech
OL,9,Freprimanding young Nigerian women for
OL,10,Fdressing indecently and accusing them
OL,11,Fof mimicking "film stars from America".
OL,13,F"They don't know where they come from.
OL,14,FWhy did Meghan come here, looking for
OL,15,FAfrica? That is something we have to
OL,16,Ftake home with. We know who we are and
OL,17,Fdon't lose who you are," she said.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@fO]uD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
