OL,3,CKing to honour Nigerian president with
OL,4,CWindsor Castle state banquet
OL,6,FThe first lady's office said she was
OL,7,Fnot talking about Meghan's outfits,
OL,8,Fbut that she "meant Meghan appreciates
OL,9,Fthe people we are and hence her coming
OL,10,Fhere".
OL,26,@pD@NOUrD@EO]
